address.gui

Class GUI

  • java.lang.Object
    • address.gui.GUI
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    GUIAddAddress, GUIFindNote, GUINewNotes, GUINotes

    public class GUI
extends java.lang.Object
    The main GUI class that holds its immediate sub windows objects and calls for there creation. This class sets up the frame and elements for the opening window for the application.
    Author:
    Jialiang Zhong
